nodes.text: Dirty Dozen: The Imperial Grand Admirals

Dirty Dozen: The Imperial Grand Admirals was an article by Daniel Wallace and Abel G. Peña for Star Wars Gamer magazine. The article included biographies and roleplaying statistics about the Grand Admirals of the Galactic Empire. After Gamer was canceled, Wallace and Peña adapted much of the article for the Star Wars Insider 66 article Who's Who: Imperial Grand Admirals.
